videos.description: Sean White pass intercepted Kivon Coman return for 16 yds to the Aub 19

videos.headline: Auburn strikes first with short TD pass
videos.description: Auburn QB Sean White finds Ryan Davis for a simple 3-yard touchdown pass, giving the Tigers the lead over Mississippi State.

videos.headline: K. Pettway run for 1 yd for a TD,
videos.description: Kamryn Pettway run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Auburn recovers ball after strip sack
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald is strip sacked by Auburn's Marlon Davidson and it is recovered by Montravius Adams, giving Tigers possession of the ball once again.

videos.headline: Auburn RB Pettway 3-yard score gives Tigers a three TD lead
videos.description: Auburn RB Kamryn Pettway runs through the Mississippi State defensive line for 3-yard touchdown run, giving the Tigers a 21-0 lead.

videos.headline: Pettway puts Auburn up big with third rushing TD
videos.description: Auburn RB Kamryn Pettway cannot be stopped by Mississippi State's defense, scoring his third rushing touchdown in the first half to increase the Tigers' lead.

videos.headline: Auburn's domination continues with strip sack return for TD
videos.description: Auburn's Carl Lawson forces Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald to fumble, which is picked up by Montravius Adams and returned for a 13-yard touchdown run, putting the Tigers up by five scores.
